lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps won the 100-meter butterfly at his first meet in eight months, beginning his push to compete at a fifth Olympics next year.

headline.main: In Return, Phelps First in Qualifying

abstract: Michael Phelps wins 100-meter butterfly at Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Mesa, Ariz.
